net.akaish.kitty.orm.dumputils.migrations

Class KittyORMVersionFileDumpMigrator

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.akaish.kitty.orm.dumputils.migrations.KittyORMVersionMigrator
      • net.akaish.kitty.orm.dumputils.migrations.KittyORMVersionFileDumpMigrator

  • public class KittyORMVersionFileDumpMigrator
extends KittyORMVersionMigrator
    File dump migrator implementation
    This migrator looks for all files in specified directory and creates KittyMigration from
    them if possible (files are files with name in x-x-x-x.sql pattern, where 'x' are positive integers that
    are ranges, e.g. minLower-minUpper-maxLower-maxUpper ranges of current migrations scripts) Created by akaish on 05.03.18.
